channel.title: Trap Tapes V.I (prod. SurfSoundMusic) feat. Papamitrou
channel.description:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SV_w8zGUECU&list=PLXYkr_ueMeEBQC2D25b3BlvLHoADPCvWb
Above is a link to my latest project. It’s a trap/ rap beat tape so the beats are more simplistic, and loop-y. Critiquing is highly welcomed, but I ask that in return, if you could tell me our favorite track, and why. Thanks! -SurfSoundMusic

item.title: Trap Tapes V.I (prod. SurfSoundMusic) feat. Papamitrou
item.dc:creator: WAVZ
item.description:
Personally, I feel like I still have to find the right combination of drum kits for this genre, and although it was a small project, I could’ve lengthened the tracks a bit more. My favorite is Outro. It uses sounds that I never used previously in my projects, and I feel like it bumps pretty hard! Haha
